{"data":[{"id":560535396,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a6772f76824a8d8405ae2e63730a5ed0","url_token":"yu-qi-34-98","name":"币圈二佬","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d3a4d1389322061af243ce224b761cc8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d3a4d1389322061af243ce224b761cc8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a6772f76824a8d8405ae2e63730a5ed0","user_type":"people","headline":"公众号也是这个名字，哈哈。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":92,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560535396","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545852232,"updated_time":1545852232,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":81,"comment_count":17,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e  我理解你的状态，如果你真的喜欢数学，热爱数学，静下心来听一听别人的建议，在你这个年纪，可以像这样对待自己喜欢的东西是可贵的也是稀少的，你有天分是肯定的，可是这个世界不会像你而倾斜，你眼里的哥德巴赫猜想，或许和别人眼里的哥德巴赫猜想，不是一回事，但是你也看到了它的美不是吗，数学在逻辑上的美是纯净的不可挑剔的。如果你成功了，可能你真的是个天才，用的方法可能和前人完全不一样，会给我们展示另一种美。如果你失败了，那么就是你现在坚持的东西还不够严谨，也就是说还不够完美。那你要像着完美走去。不论结果怎样，我希望你能始终保持这份热爱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e   有人说你不知天高地厚，那你要清楚你凭什么不知天高地厚，凭接的就是你这一份热爱，以及虔诚。爱因斯坦在16岁就在思考光速下电磁波会如何，种下了一颗种子，这颗种子，在10年后开花叫做狭义相对论，又过了10年结果叫做广义相对论。他在少年时的想法，用了最宝贵的青春去论证。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e   如果成功最好，如果失败不也就是告诉别人我这么搞，走到这里走不通了啊，当年陈景润也是做的这个事。所以我希望不论结果怎样，你都能保持这份热爱，并且在你心里让种子发芽，能持续的发光发热，不要去怪制度也不要去恨什么，用你的青春，用你的时间，用你的孤独，去看看种子长成参天大树后的样子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e   我觉得应该多给这种孩子一点宽容，他没有去抽烟喝酒蹦迪打架斗殴，只是看到王冠上的宝石太漂亮太耀眼，想去摸一摸罢了，也挺可爱的。为什么只有丹麦的小女孩卖火柴才是童话呢。在国内因为现实因素生活放弃了对科研追求的人不少，最终只能成为芸芸众生。这个孩子还不用去考虑那么多，哪怕是场梦，让他多做一会儿，让他自己醒过来，可能更会多那么一点些许的善意。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我理解你的状态，如果你真的喜欢数学，热爱数学，静下心来听一听别人的建议，在你这个年纪，可以像这样对待自己喜欢的东西是可贵的也是稀少的，你有天分是肯定的，可是这个世界不会像你而倾斜，你眼里的哥德巴赫猜想，或许和别人眼里的哥德巴赫猜想，不是一…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=92\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_aut